description: Indulge in the epitome of luxury with this remarkable South Boston penthouse in the Allele. Discover a spacious haven boasting two luxurious bedrooms and two stylishly appointed bathrooms. The stunning kitchen seamlessly flows into an open floor plan, offering panoramic city vistas and basking the interior in natural light through expansive windows. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary with a private ensuite bathroom. Furthermore, this penthouse provides the convenience of deeded garage parking and the exclusivity of a private roof deck, creating a harmonious fusion of comfort and elegance. Seize the chance to elevate your lifestyle in this exceptional residence!
